## EXECUTIONER GRADIENTS

### The Blade's Edge
```
linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0A0A 0%, #C0C0C0 50%, #8B0000 100%)
CSS: background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0A0A 0%, #C0C0C0 50%, #8B0000 100%);
Usage: Obsidian blade with blood edge
Warning: May cause spontaneous execution urges
```

### The Pyramid At Midnight
```
linear-gradient(180deg, #1A0A1A 0%, #4A4A4A 50%, #0A0A0A 100%)
CSS: background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1A0A1A 0%, #4A4A4A 50%, #0A0A0A 100%);
Usage: Pyramid temple at 3AM ritual
Warning: The pyramid is watching
```

### The Ritual Smoke
```
repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #660066, #660066 10px, #0A0A0A 10px, #0A0A0A 20px)
CSS: background: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #660066, #660066 10px, #0A0A0A 10px, #0A0A0A 20px);
Usage: Toxic purple smoke from sacrifice
Warning: Actual ritual smoke may appear
```

### The Verdict
```
radial-gradient(circle, #8B0000 0%, #0A0A0A 100%)
CSS: background: radial-gradient(circle, #8B0000 0%, #0A0A0A 100%);
Usage: Blood verdict spreading into void
Warning: The verdict is final
```

### The Executioner's Blessing
```
linear-gradient(90deg, #FFD700 0%, #660066 50%, #0A0A0A 100%)
CSS: background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FFD700 0%, #660066 50%, #0A0A0A 100%);
Usage: Quetzalcoatl's blessing on the execution
Warning: Divine judgment confirmed
```

